### ==================== ADMIN API TESTS ====================
### All endpoints require ADMIN role

### 1. Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:54955/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@gmail.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### ==================== USER MANAGEMENT ====================

### 2. Get all users
GET http://localhost:54955/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:54955/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update user role (change user to ADMIN)
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/admin/users/2/role?role=ADMIN
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Update user role (change user back to USER)
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/admin/users/2/role?role=USER
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Enable/disable user
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/admin/users/2/status?enabled=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Delete user (be careful!)
DELETE http://localhost:54955/api/admin/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== ORDER MANAGEMENT ====================

### 8. Get all orders
GET http://localhost:54955/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get orders by status
GET http://localhost:54955/api/admin/orders/status/PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Update order status
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/admin/orders/1/status?status=CONFIRMED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Update payment status
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/admin/orders/1/payment?paymentStatus=PAID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Add tracking number
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/admin/orders/1/tracking?trackingNumber=1Z999AA10123456784
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== DASHBOARD STATISTICS ====================

### 13. Get dashboard stats
GET http://localhost:54955/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}